New Records: De'Aaron Fox set a new season-high with 49 points, surpassing DeMarcus Cousins' franchise record for most points over a two-game span
Key Match Events: De'Aaron Fox led the Sacramento Kings to a 121-117 win over the Utah Jazz
The Jazz opened the third quarter with a 10-3 run and led 94-90 at the end of the frame
Sacramento came back in the fourth to take a 118-116 lead on a Jordan McLaughlin 3 with a minute left to play
